# topology

This file is a placeholder for the Cisco Packet Tracer simulation file (`topology.pkt`).

## How to Obtain

1. Open Cisco Packet Tracer 8.x or later.
2. Build the topology described in [README.md](README.md).
3. Save the file as `topology.pkt` in this directory.

Alternatively, export the topology from an existing Packet Tracer project and place it here.
